Singer Omah Lay has dedicated a portion of his new song ‘woman’ to the love between ace singer Tu Face Idibia and his wife Annie Macualay Idibia. The ace singer in 2020 described himself Omah Lay’s number one fan, referring to him as a bundle of talents that cannot be hidden.   Why I’m no longer friendly with Liquorose-Maria     Reactions as Tems smokes at US vacation     How Adesua saved my daughter from bullies, by Ireti Doyle   The African queen singer said: “True talent no fit hide. Omah lay to the world!!! I humbly claim the title of #1 fan. Abeg make nobody follow me drag am.” Moved by this allegiance, the singer dedicated a portion of the song to Tu Face and his wife. The portion reads: “All of a sudden, she say me and her go be Tuface Annie Macaulay.”